Package org.moddingx.launcherlib.mappings

Class MappingWriter

java.lang.Object
org.moddingx.launcherlib.mappings.visitor.MappingVisitor
org.moddingx.launcherlib.mappings.MappingWriter
public class MappingWriter extends MappingVisitor
A MappingVisitor that assembles an IMappingFile from the things it visits. If the same class/field/method in the original name set is visited twice, the first visit will be used.
